00:46:44.501 --> 00:46:55.612 line:90% position:50% align:center
With Jehovah to guide us in all that we do,
How I love to be truly in love

00:46:55.612 --> 00:47:09.259 line:90% position:50% align:center
With someone like you,
Someone like you.

00:47:09.259 --> 00:47:20.304 line:90% position:50% align:center
How I love to be truly in love
With someone like you.

00:47:24.408 --> 00:47:28.812 line:90% position:50% align:center
So many of our brothers and sisters 
can agree with the words of that song: 

00:47:29.580 --> 00:47:33.617 line:90% position:50% align:center
“With a threefold cord, love will grow.” 

00:47:34.651 --> 00:47:37.821 line:90% position:50% align:center
In marriage, in youth, 

00:47:37.821 --> 00:47:40.224 line:90% position:50% align:center
really, in all things we’ve considered, 

00:47:40.224 --> 00:47:43.126 line:90% position:50% align:center
Jehovah will be there to guide us. 

00:47:43.126 --> 00:47:45.195 line:90% position:50% align:center
What will be the result? 

00:47:45.195 --> 00:47:47.898 line:90% position:50% align:center
We’ll find the warmth and security 

00:47:47.898 --> 00:47:50.200 line:90% position:50% align:center
of being securely wrapped 

00:47:50.200 --> 00:47:52.436 line:90% position:50% align:center
in Jehovah’s “bag of life.” 

00:47:53.737 --> 00:47:56.073 line:90% position:50% align:center
We hope you enjoyed our program. 

00:47:56.073 --> 00:47:57.574 line:90% position:50% align:center
We conclude by heading 

00:47:57.574 --> 00:48:00.444 line:90% position:50% align:center
to the beautiful tropical island 
of Sri Lanka, 

00:48:00.444 --> 00:48:03.814 line:90% position:50% align:center
off the southeast coast 
of India in the Indian Ocean. 

00:48:05.449 --> 00:48:09.653 line:90% position:50% align:center
Over 6,000 publishers 
make up the 112 congregations on the island, 

00:48:09.653 --> 00:48:12.689 line:90% position:50% align:center
including 13 isolated groups. 

00:48:12.689 --> 00:48:14.992 line:90% position:50% align:center
As you travel throughout the country, 

00:48:14.992 --> 00:48:18.829 line:90% position:50% align:center
the scars of the decades-long civil war 
are still evident. 

00:48:18.829 --> 00:48:21.965 line:90% position:50% align:center
However, our brothers and sisters display 

00:48:21.965 --> 00:48:24.968 line:90% position:50% align:center
the beautiful spirit of Christian unity. 

00:48:24.968 --> 00:48:27.504 line:90% position:50% align:center
Publishers preach the good news 
to those on the coast, 

00:48:28.005 --> 00:48:30.007 line:90% position:50% align:center
high in the mountains, 

00:48:30.007 --> 00:48:33.043 line:90% position:50% align:center
and in the bustling cities. 

00:48:33.043 --> 00:48:35.879 line:90% position:50% align:center
More than 8,000 Bible studies 
are being conducted, 

00:48:35.879 --> 00:48:39.883 line:90% position:50% align:center
and over 650 brothers and sisters 
are in the pioneer work. 

00:48:39.883 --> 00:48:43.754 line:90% position:50% align:center
Because of the dense population 
in the city of Colombo, 

00:48:43.754 --> 00:48:48.759 line:90% position:50% align:center
those in metropolitan witnessing 
see an average of almost 17,000 people 

00:48:48.759 --> 00:48:51.328 line:90% position:50% align:center
in just one 8-hour period. 

00:48:52.296 --> 00:48:54.631 line:90% position:50% align:center
High in Sri Lanka’s tea mountains 

00:48:54.631 --> 00:48:58.969 line:90% position:50% align:center
is a small congregation 
in the town of Badulla. 

00:48:58.969 --> 00:49:02.205 line:90% position:50% align:center
Their productive ministry takes them 
into banana plantations, 

00:49:02.205 --> 00:49:05.642 line:90% position:50% align:center
jungles, and mountain tea estates 
as they search 

00:49:05.642 --> 00:49:08.478 line:90% position:50% align:center
for those receptive to the good news. 

00:49:08.478 --> 00:49:11.315 line:90% position:50% align:center
Despite differing ethnic backgrounds, 

00:49:11.315 --> 00:49:15.118 line:90% position:50% align:center
they’re completely united 
in worship and brotherly affection. 

00:49:15.118 --> 00:49:17.587 line:90% position:50% align:center
Our brothers and sisters 
who are wrapped up 

00:49:17.587 --> 00:49:19.589 line:90% position:50% align:center
in Jehovah’s “bag of life” 

00:49:19.589 --> 00:49:21.591 line:90% position:50% align:center
send you their warm love and greetings 

00:49:21.591 --> 00:49:23.760 line:90% position:50% align:center
from the mountaintops of Sri Lanka! 

00:49:23.760 --> 00:49:25.862 line:90% position:50% align:center
Thank you for watching. 

00:49:25.862 --> 00:49:28.532 line:90% position:50% align:center
From the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses, 

00:49:28.532 --> 00:49:31.068 line:90% position:50% align:center
this is JW Broadcasting. 

